h1 Talks at meetups, conferences & more
- each talk in public._data.talks
  .media
    .media-body
      .media-heading
        | #{talk.title + ' | '}
        a(href="#{talk.eventUrl}", target="_blank", rel="noopener noreferrer")= talk.event
      .media-content
        | #{talk.description}
        br
        i.fa.fa-clock-o
        | #{' ' + talk.date}
        br
        - each link, index in talk.links
          a(href="#{link.url}", target="_blank", rel="noopener noreferrer")= link.label
          if index < (talk.links.length - 1)
            | #{' | '}

br

h1 Projects
- each project in public._data.projects
  .media
    .media-body
      .media-heading= project.title.toUpperCase()
      .media-content
        | #{project.description}
        br
        if project.url
          a(href="#{project.url}", target="_blank", rel="noopener noreferrer") view
        if project.repo
          if project.url
            | #{' | '}
          a(href="#{project.repo}", target="_blank", rel="noopener noreferrer") repo
